      "title": "Z-Image + IZT LoRA + 6 full bodies",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Z-Image Turbo + **CharacterDesignIZT** + **ControlNet Canny**\n\nLayout: **6 full body** с разными эмоциями (сетка 3×2, 1024×1024).\n\n### Модели\n| Файл | Папка |\n|------|--------|\n| `qwen_3_4b.safetensors` | `text_encoders/` |\n| `z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors` | `diffusion_models/` |\n| `ae.safetensors` | `vae/` |\n| `Z-Image-Turbo-Fun-Controlnet-Union.safetensors` | `model_patches/` |\n| Character Design IZT LoRA | `loras/` |\n\n### Шаблон layout\n1. Скопируйте `workflows/comfyui/assets/char_sheet_layout_6fullbody_expr.png` → `ComfyUI/input/`\n2. Координаты нарезки: `char_sheet_layout_6fullbody_expr.crops.json`\n\n### Настройки\n- **LoRA strength:** 0.7 · **ControlNet strength:** 0.9\n- **Steps:** 8 · **CFG:** 1 · **1024×1024**\n- **Триггер:** `CharacterDesignIZT`\n\nMarinara API: `z-image-turbo-character-design-izt-controlnet-6fullbody.api.json`\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
